┌ Help (Esc to close) ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│sipnab v0.1.0-alpha — Keyboard Shortcuts                                      │
│                                                                              │
│Navigation:                                                                   │
│  ↑/↓ or j/k        Scroll list / view                                        │
│  Enter             Open selected item                                        │
│  Esc               Go back to previous view                                  │
